::GoldenEye::

She looked at Tails.
"If you want, I shall fly you to where ever you wish to go.  I'll let 
you follow your destiny my friend." She gave a heavy sigh.
She didn't want to let her one and only friend to have to go down 
into the war zone and possably get killed. But she couldn't fight 
against one's instincts.
"Just tell me and I'll take you there."
